values: There's no way in hell I'm wearing that again

schools work is done for today, I gotta stop by at the workshop and then I think I'm gonna check what that punk Hans is doing
work's good, school's even better. I think I'm starting to feel what being fine is all about.
Being a letterer is not as bad as I thought, I get to paint all day,

School is nice. I have to make five drawings for wednesday, of body parts

...I need a model.

Hans and I picked up the tests and turns out I, we have funny mono, isn't that a very good joke?

anyway, doc gave us meds and I don't feel as bad as yesterday, yay for it

I don't feel ok, I'm so tired and I think it's the flu, I told that moron I was gonna get sick with his damned cold water.

I went to the tests thing with him.

And now we wait.

Alright, I'm confused, I think I just started a relationship and I don't want it, I'm gonna end up fucking things up, I just know it. This should teach me to keep my bloody mouth shut.

 NO!, I don't want to let him in, I don't want us to be exclusive, I don't want to want him, damn, I don't want anyone else.

I think I'm scared.

Before he left he told me to meet him at the hospital at noon. I didn't go, I couldn't, I'm kinda hiding, maybe he'll just forget it and move on.

"the man had killed the thing he loved and so he had to die"

this is just wrong.

Yestarday I woke up around 5:00 am. showered, left Hans' and went to work -I enter at 6:00- when I get there, the girl from the other shift is nowhere to be seen so I go to the back room to change (there's no way in hell I'm walking out in the street with that fucking Oxxo uniform); so, I've undressed when she bursts into the room.

At first she rushed to apologize and all that rubbish, but then she didn't leave, so, oh my god, anyway, I was at it with her when I realized what the fuck I was doing, so I just pushed her away, half dressed and got the hell out.

I went looking for Hans but he was already gone.

Well, I guess I don't have a job anymore.

ok, I'm frustrated, I write a ten pages story and when I finish it I realize it is a piece of shit.

"Night was not coming today" What kind of crap is that?

Ended up getting matches and setting that rubbish on fire. Went out and shagged the first decent guy I could find.

I know there must be something wrong with me, but i just don't want to accept it.

ok, I talked to Hans today, fight with him would be a better word, any way, i kinda said things I didn't mean, I made him mad and then I get mad because he was mad *sigh* I hate my life and I hate that bloody kid
ok, so this is it... I'm panicking, but anyway, I'm here just because Hans made me, so I hope to get it in a bit
